description: Deutschland808 offers a new heathy, hearty set of soups made fresh everyday. Our old family recipes have been brought from the heart of Germany to heart of Honolulu. Now taste the flavors of Oma's kitchen, with a twist for today's palate. To accompany these delicious family traditions, try our beer brats with a nicely toasted homemade brotchen. We invite you to be a part of our family and spread the love of good German food.
name: Deutschland808
